# W-Rift-Mechanic-Plumbing — DONE
Completed: 2026-05-02

## Tunables (frozen on WG.HuntPickups.RIFT_TUNABLES)

| Tunable | Value | Note |
|---|---|---|
| RIFT_SIGIL_DROP_RATE_BOSS | 1.0 | Wraith Father (stage 18) always drops 1 on clear |
| RIFT_SIGIL_DROP_RATE_STAGE_CLEAR | 0.01 | 1% per eldritch stage clear (stages 16–18) |

Both rolls fire independently on stage 18 clear: boss drop (guaranteed) + stage-clear roll (1%).
Stages 16 and 17 have no boss drop — stage-clear roll only.

## Drop state

- `WG.State.get().rift.sigils` — cumulative integer counter.
- `Math.floor(sigils / 3)` = unlocked guest slots.
- Sigils never consumed — progress is cumulative.
- Grant path: `wg-game.js finishHunt(true)` → `WG.HuntPickups.rollSigilDrop(stageId, bossDefeated)` → `state.rift.sigils += count` + `WG.Engine.emit('rift:sigil-found', ...)`.

## Files changed

| File | Change |
|---|---|
| `js/relics/relics-catalog.js` | Added `rift_sigil` (legendary, `equippable:false`, `stat:null`, `value:0`) |
| `js/relics/relics-equip.js` | Guard: rejects equip if `r.equippable === false` |
| `js/core/wg-state.js` | Added `rift: { sigils: 0 }` to state schema |
| `js/hunt/hunt-pickups.js` | Added `RIFT_TUNABLES`, `rollSigilDrop()`, exposed both on `WG.HuntPickups` |
| `js/wg-game.js` | `finishHunt`: calls `rollSigilDrop`, grants sigils to state, emits `rift:sigil-found` |
| `js/hunt/hunt-results.js` | Shows `🔮 ×N Rift Sigil` in rewards row when sigils drop |
| `js/ascend/ascend-render.js` | Added "RIFT GUESTS" collapsible section (default collapsed) |

